author: Katie Simpson,Alexander Panetta
title: G7 ministers spike joint statement on COVID-19 after U.S. demands it be called 'Wuhan virus'
description: Any hope of G7 foreign ministers releasing a joint statement on the fight against COVID-19 was killed today after the U.S. insisted the document refer to it as the “Wuhan virus."
content:
